{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 13,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 712.876,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.111,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the angel spake unto me, saying:",
      "verse": "13:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 3.291,
      "end": 4.127,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look!",
      "verse": "13:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 4.307,
      "end": 7.233,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked and beheld many nations and kingdoms.",
      "verse": "13:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 7.913,
      "end": 9.724,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said unto me:",
      "verse": "13:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 9.904,
      "end": 11.251,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "What beholdest thou?",
      "verse": "13:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 11.431,
      "end": 12.638,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said:",
      "verse": "13:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 12.818,
      "end": 15.558,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I behold many nations and kingdoms.",
      "verse": "13:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 16.238,
      "end": 17.771,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said unto me:",
      "verse": "13:3",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 17.951,
      "end": 20.645,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "These are the nations and kingdoms of the Gentiles.",
      "verse": "13:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 21.325,
      "end": 25.319,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I saw among the nations of the Gentiles",
      "verse": "13:4",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 25.499,
      "end": 27.867,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the formation of a great church.",
      "verse": "13:4",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 28.547,
      "end": 30.358,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said unto me:",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 30.538,
      "end": 32.86,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold the formation of a church",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 33.04,
      "end": 36.802,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is most abominable above all other churches,",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 36.982,
      "end": 39.304,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which slayeth the saints of God,",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 39.484,
      "end": 42.503,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and tortureth them and bindeth them down,",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 42.683,
      "end": 45.33,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and yoketh them with a yoke of iron,",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 45.51,
      "end": 47.971,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and bringeth them down into captivity.",
      "verse": "13:5",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 48.651,
      "end": 52.784,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beheld this great and abominable church;",
      "verse": "13:6",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 52.964,
      "end": 54.682,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw the devil",
      "verse": "13:6",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 54.862,
      "end": 57.045,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he was the founder of it.",
      "verse": "13:6",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 57.725,
      "end": 60.093,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I also saw gold, and silver,",
      "verse": "13:7",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 60.273,
      "end": 63.71,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and silks, and scarlets, and fine-twined linen,",
      "verse": "13:7",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 63.89,
      "end": 66.026,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all manner of precious clothing;",
      "verse": "13:7",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 66.206,
      "end": 67.924,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw many harlots.",
      "verse": "13:7",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 68.604,
      "end": 70.787,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel spake unto me, saying:",
      "verse": "13:8",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 70.967,
      "end": 73.01,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold the gold, and the silver,",
      "verse": "13:8",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 73.19,
      "end": 77.137,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the silks, and the scarlets, and the fine-twined linen,",
      "verse": "13:8",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 77.317,
      "end": 80.057,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the precious clothing, and the harlots,",
      "verse": "13:8",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 80.237,
      "end": 83.395,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are the desires of this great and abominable church.",
      "verse": "13:8",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 84.075,
      "end": 86.536,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also for the praise of the world",
      "verse": "13:9",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 86.716,
      "end": 88.899,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "do they destroy the saints of God,",
      "verse": "13:9",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 89.079,
      "end": 91.401,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and bring them down into captivity.",
      "verse": "13:9",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 92.081,
      "end": 95.471,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I looked and beheld many waters;",
      "verse": "13:10",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 95.651,
      "end": 99.273,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they divided the Gentiles from the seed of my brethren.",
      "verse": "13:10",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 99.953,
      "end": 103.111,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the angel said unto me:",
      "verse": "13:11",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 103.291,
      "end": 106.449,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold the wrath of God is upon the seed of thy brethren.",
      "verse": "13:11",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 107.129,
      "end": 110.24,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked and beheld a man among the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:12",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 110.42,
      "end": 114.414,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who was separated from the seed of my brethren by the many waters;",
      "verse": "13:12",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 114.594,
      "end": 117.009,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I beheld the Spirit of God,",
      "verse": "13:12",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 117.189,
      "end": 119.975,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it came down and wrought upon the man;",
      "verse": "13:12",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 120.155,
      "end": 122.849,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he went forth upon the many waters,",
      "verse": "13:12",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 123.029,
      "end": 125.351,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even unto the seed of my brethren,",
      "verse": "13:12",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 125.531,
      "end": 127.296,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who were in the promised land.",
      "verse": "13:12",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 127.976,
      "end": 131.227,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beheld the Spirit of God,",
      "verse": "13:13",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 131.407,
      "end": 133.729,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it wrought upon other Gentiles;",
      "verse": "13:13",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 133.909,
      "end": 136.37,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they went forth out of captivity,",
      "verse": "13:13",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 136.55,
      "end": 138.175,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon the many waters.",
      "verse": "13:13",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 138.855,
      "end": 141.177,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beheld",
      "verse": "13:14",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 141.357,
      "end": 144.886,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many multitudes of the Gentiles upon the land of promise;",
      "verse": "13:14",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 145.066,
      "end": 147.388,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I beheld the wrath of God,",
      "verse": "13:14",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 147.568,
      "end": 150.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it was upon the seed of my brethren;",
      "verse": "13:14",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 150.395,
      "end": 153.692,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were scattered before the Gentiles and were smitten.",
      "verse": "13:14",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 154.372,
      "end": 156.694,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I beheld the Spirit of the Lord,",
      "verse": "13:15",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 156.874,
      "end": 160.218,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it was upon the Gentiles, and they did prosper",
      "verse": "13:15",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 160.398,
      "end": 163.138,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and obtain the land for their inheritance;",
      "verse": "13:15",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 163.318,
      "end": 165.733,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I beheld that they were white,",
      "verse": "13:15",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 165.913,
      "end": 168.281,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and exceedingly fair and beautiful,",
      "verse": "13:15",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 168.461,
      "end": 170.969,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "like unto my people before they were slain.",
      "verse": "13:15",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 171.649,
      "end": 178.104,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, beheld that the Gentiles who had gone forth out of captivity",
      "verse": "13:16",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 178.284,
      "end": 180.513,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "did humble themselves before the Lord;",
      "verse": "13:16",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 180.693,
      "end": 182.969,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the power of the Lord was with them.",
      "verse": "13:16",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 183.649,
      "end": 189.454,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I beheld that their mother Gentiles were gathered together upon the waters,",
      "verse": "13:17",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 189.634,
      "end": 192.653,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and upon the land also, to battle against them.",
      "verse": "13:17",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 193.333,
      "end": 196.677,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I beheld that the power of God was with them,",
      "verse": "13:18",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 196.857,
      "end": 200.572,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also that the wrath of God was upon all those",
      "verse": "13:18",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 200.752,
      "end": 204.328,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that were gathered together against them to battle.",
      "verse": "13:18",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 205.008,
      "end": 209.466,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, beheld that the Gentiles that had gone out of captivity",
      "verse": "13:19",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 209.646,
      "end": 212.247,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "were delivered by the power of God",
      "verse": "13:19",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 212.427,
      "end": 215.121,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "out of the hands of all other nations.",
      "verse": "13:19",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 215.801,
      "end": 221.095,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, beheld that they did prosper in the land;",
      "verse": "13:20",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 221.275,
      "end": 222.854,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I beheld a book,",
      "verse": "13:20",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 223.034,
      "end": 225.495,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it was carried forth among them.",
      "verse": "13:20",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 226.175,
      "end": 227.986,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said unto me:",
      "verse": "13:21",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 228.166,
      "end": 230.256,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Knowest thou the meaning of the book?",
      "verse": "13:21",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 230.936,
      "end": 232.515,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said unto him:",
      "verse": "13:22",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 232.695,
      "end": 233.902,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I know not.",
      "verse": "13:22",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 234.582,
      "end": 235.789,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said:",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 235.969,
      "end": 238.802,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold it proceedeth out of the mouth of a Jew.",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 238.982,
      "end": 240.7,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, beheld it;",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 240.88,
      "end": 242.552,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he said unto me:",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 242.732,
      "end": 246.354,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "The book that thou beholdest is a record of the Jews,",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 246.534,
      "end": 249.413,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which contains the covenants of the Lord,",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 249.593,
      "end": 252.704,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he hath made unto the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 252.884,
      "end": 257.667,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it also containeth many of the prophecies of the holy prophets;",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 257.847,
      "end": 260.68,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it is a record like unto the engravings",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 260.86,
      "end": 263.043,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are upon the plates of brass,",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 263.223,
      "end": 265.266,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save there are not so many;",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 265.446,
      "end": 268.79,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, they contain the covenants of the Lord,",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 268.97,
      "end": 272.081,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he hath made unto the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 272.261,
      "end": 275.28,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they are of great worth unto the Gentiles.",
      "verse": "13:23",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 275.96,
      "end": 278.375,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel of the Lord said unto me:",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 278.555,
      "end": 283.338,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Thou hast beheld that the book proceeded forth from the mouth of a Jew;",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 283.518,
      "end": 286.537,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and when it proceeded forth from the mouth of a Jew",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 286.717,
      "end": 289.921,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it contained the fulness of the gospel of the Lord,",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 290.101,
      "end": 292.562,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of whom the twelve apostles bear record;",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 292.742,
      "end": 294.367,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they bear record",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 294.547,
      "end": 297.426,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the truth which is in the Lamb of God.",
      "verse": "13:24",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 298.106,
      "end": 303.679,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, these things go forth from the Jews in purity unto the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:25",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 303.859,
      "end": 306.088,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the truth which is in God.",
      "verse": "13:25",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 306.768,
      "end": 310.948,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they go forth by the hand of the twelve apostles of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 311.128,
      "end": 313.45,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the Jews unto the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 313.63,
      "end": 317.995,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "thou seest the formation of that great and abominable church,",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 318.175,
      "end": 321.426,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is most abominable above all other churches;",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 321.606,
      "end": 325.414,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, they have taken away from the gospel of the Lamb",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 325.594,
      "end": 328.334,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many parts which are plain and most precious;",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 328.514,
      "end": 331.997,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also many covenants of the Lord have they taken away.",
      "verse": "13:26",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 332.677,
      "end": 334.163,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And all this have they done",
      "verse": "13:27",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 334.343,
      "end": 337.454,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they might pervert the right ways of the Lord,",
      "verse": "13:27",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 337.634,
      "end": 340.095,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they might blind the eyes",
      "verse": "13:27",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 340.275,
      "end": 343.247,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and harden the hearts of the children of men.",
      "verse": "13:27",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 343.927,
      "end": 345.552,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, thou seest",
      "verse": "13:28",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 345.732,
      "end": 347.822,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that after the book hath gone forth",
      "verse": "13:28",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 348.002,
      "end": 351.392,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "through the hands of the great and abominable church,",
      "verse": "13:28",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 351.572,
      "end": 356.82,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that there are many plain and precious things taken away from the book,",
      "verse": "13:28",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 357.0,
      "end": 359.415,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the book of the Lamb of God.",
      "verse": "13:28",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 360.095,
      "end": 363.671,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after these plain and precious things were taken away",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 363.851,
      "end": 367.009,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it goeth forth unto all the nations of the Gentiles;",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 367.189,
      "end": 370.997,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after it goeth forth unto all the nations of the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 371.177,
      "end": 374.614,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even across the many waters which thou hast seen",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 374.794,
      "end": 378.509,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with the Gentiles which have gone forth out of captivity,",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 378.689,
      "end": 382.218,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "thou seest\u2014 because of the many plain and precious things",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 382.398,
      "end": 384.813,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been taken out of the book,",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 384.993,
      "end": 389.591,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were plain unto the understanding of the children of men,",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 389.771,
      "end": 392.975,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the plainness which is in the Lamb of God\u2014",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 393.155,
      "end": 395.988,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of these things which are taken away",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 396.168,
      "end": 398.072,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "out of the gospel of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 398.252,
      "end": 400.713,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a exceedingly great many do stumble,",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 400.893,
      "end": 404.097,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, insomuch that Satan hath great power over them.",
      "verse": "13:29",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 404.777,
      "end": 407.749,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Nevertheless, thou beholdest that the Gentiles",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 407.929,
      "end": 410.53,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who have gone forth out of captivity,",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 410.71,
      "end": 415.586,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and have been lifted up by the power of God above all other nations,",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 415.766,
      "end": 417.67,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon the face of the land",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 417.85,
      "end": 420.126,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is choice above all other lands,",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 420.306,
      "end": 424.532,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the land that the Lord God hath covenanted with thy father",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 424.712,
      "end": 428.102,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that his seed should have for the land of their inheritance;",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 428.282,
      "end": 431.486,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, thou seest that the Lord God will not suffer",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 431.666,
      "end": 436.403,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Gentiles will utterly destroy the mixture of thy seed,",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 436.583,
      "end": 438.812,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are among thy brethren.",
      "verse": "13:30",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 439.492,
      "end": 441.117,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Neither will he suffer",
      "verse": "13:31",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 441.297,
      "end": 445.012,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Gentiles shall destroy the seed of thy brethren.",
      "verse": "13:31",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 445.692,
      "end": 447.735,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Neither will the Lord God suffer",
      "verse": "13:32",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 447.915,
      "end": 453.116,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Gentiles shall forever remain in that awful state of blindness,",
      "verse": "13:32",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 453.296,
      "end": 455.339,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which thou beholdest they are in,",
      "verse": "13:32",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 455.519,
      "end": 459.977,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the plain and most precious parts of the gospel of the Lamb",
      "verse": "13:32",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 460.157,
      "end": 463.594,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been kept back by that abominable church,",
      "verse": "13:32",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 463.774,
      "end": 465.957,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose formation thou hast seen.",
      "verse": "13:32",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 466.637,
      "end": 468.959,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore saith the Lamb of God:",
      "verse": "13:33",
      "lineIndex": 153
    },
    {
      "start": 469.139,
      "end": 471.554,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will be merciful unto the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:33",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 471.734,
      "end": 477.214,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the visiting of the remnant of the house of Israel in great judgment.",
      "verse": "13:33",
      "lineIndex": 155
    },
    {
      "start": 477.894,
      "end": 481.377,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the angel of the Lord spake unto me, saying:",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 156
    },
    {
      "start": 481.557,
      "end": 483.647,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, saith the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 157
    },
    {
      "start": 483.827,
      "end": 487.124,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after I have visited the remnant of the house of Israel\u2014",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 158
    },
    {
      "start": 487.304,
      "end": 491.344,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and this remnant of whom I speak is the seed of thy father\u2014",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 159
    },
    {
      "start": 491.524,
      "end": 495.1,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, after I have visited them in judgment,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 160
    },
    {
      "start": 495.28,
      "end": 498.206,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and smitten them by the hand of the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 161
    },
    {
      "start": 498.386,
      "end": 501.08,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after the Gentiles do stumble exceedingly,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 162
    },
    {
      "start": 501.26,
      "end": 505.207,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the most plain and precious parts of the gospel of the Lamb",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 163
    },
    {
      "start": 505.387,
      "end": 508.824,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been kept back by that abominable church,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 164
    },
    {
      "start": 509.004,
      "end": 510.815,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the mother of harlots,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 165
    },
    {
      "start": 510.995,
      "end": 512.667,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saith the Lamb\u2014",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 166
    },
    {
      "start": 512.847,
      "end": 515.912,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will be merciful unto the Gentiles in that day,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 167
    },
    {
      "start": 516.092,
      "end": 518.832,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that I will bring forth unto them,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 168
    },
    {
      "start": 519.012,
      "end": 520.637,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in mine own power,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 169
    },
    {
      "start": 520.817,
      "end": 522.35,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "much of my gospel,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 170
    },
    {
      "start": 522.53,
      "end": 524.527,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which shall be plain and precious,",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 171
    },
    {
      "start": 524.707,
      "end": 526.1,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saith the Lamb.",
      "verse": "13:34",
      "lineIndex": 172
    },
    {
      "start": 526.78,
      "end": 528.591,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For, behold, saith the Lamb:",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 173
    },
    {
      "start": 528.771,
      "end": 531.418,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will manifest myself unto thy seed,",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 174
    },
    {
      "start": 531.598,
      "end": 534.106,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they shall write many things",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 175
    },
    {
      "start": 534.286,
      "end": 536.608,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I shall minister unto them,",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 176
    },
    {
      "start": 536.788,
      "end": 539.249,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which shall be plain and precious;",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 177
    },
    {
      "start": 539.429,
      "end": 541.705,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after thy seed shall be destroyed,",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 178
    },
    {
      "start": 541.885,
      "end": 543.882,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and dwindle in unbelief,",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 179
    },
    {
      "start": 544.062,
      "end": 546.616,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the seed of thy brethren,",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 180
    },
    {
      "start": 546.796,
      "end": 549.025,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, these things shall be hid up,",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 181
    },
    {
      "start": 549.205,
      "end": 551.434,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to come forth unto the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 182
    },
    {
      "start": 551.614,
      "end": 554.261,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by the gift and power of the Lamb.",
      "verse": "13:35",
      "lineIndex": 183
    },
    {
      "start": 554.941,
      "end": 557.681,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And in them shall be written my gospel,",
      "verse": "13:36",
      "lineIndex": 184
    },
    {
      "start": 557.861,
      "end": 559.254,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "saith the Lamb",
      "verse": "13:36",
      "lineIndex": 185
    },
    {
      "start": 559.434,
      "end": 561.617,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my rock and my salvation.",
      "verse": "13:36",
      "lineIndex": 186
    },
    {
      "start": 562.297,
      "end": 563.876,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And blessed are they",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 187
    },
    {
      "start": 564.056,
      "end": 567.121,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who shall seek to bring forth my Zion at that day,",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 188
    },
    {
      "start": 567.301,
      "end": 569.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they shall have the gift",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 189
    },
    {
      "start": 569.478,
      "end": 571.521,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the power of the Holy Ghost;",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 190
    },
    {
      "start": 571.701,
      "end": 573.698,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and if they endure unto the end",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 191
    },
    {
      "start": 573.878,
      "end": 576.339,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be lifted up at the last day,",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 192
    },
    {
      "start": 576.519,
      "end": 577.912,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall be saved",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 193
    },
    {
      "start": 578.092,
      "end": 580.646,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the everlasting kingdom of the Lamb;",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 194
    },
    {
      "start": 580.826,
      "end": 582.869,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and whoso shall publish peace,",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 195
    },
    {
      "start": 583.049,
      "end": 584.907,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, tidings of great joy,",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 196
    },
    {
      "start": 585.087,
      "end": 587.827,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "how beautiful upon the mountains shall they be.",
      "verse": "13:37",
      "lineIndex": 197
    },
    {
      "start": 588.507,
      "end": 593.43,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beheld the remnant of the seed of my brethren,",
      "verse": "13:38",
      "lineIndex": 198
    },
    {
      "start": 593.61,
      "end": 596.071,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the book of the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "13:38",
      "lineIndex": 199
    },
    {
      "start": 596.251,
      "end": 598.898,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which had proceeded forth from the mouth of the Jew,",
      "verse": "13:38",
      "lineIndex": 200
    },
    {
      "start": 599.078,
      "end": 601.772,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it came forth from the Gentiles",
      "verse": "13:38",
      "lineIndex": 201
    },
    {
      "start": 601.952,
      "end": 604.924,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the remnant of the seed of my brethren.",
      "verse": "13:38",
      "lineIndex": 202
    },
    {
      "start": 605.604,
      "end": 608.019,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after it had come forth unto them",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 203
    },
    {
      "start": 608.199,
      "end": 609.917,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I beheld other books,",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 204
    },
    {
      "start": 610.097,
      "end": 612.698,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which came forth by the power of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 205
    },
    {
      "start": 612.878,
      "end": 615.014,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the Gentiles unto them,",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 206
    },
    {
      "start": 615.194,
      "end": 617.655,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the convincing of the Gentiles",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 207
    },
    {
      "start": 617.835,
      "end": 620.714,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the remnant of the seed of my brethren,",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 208
    },
    {
      "start": 620.894,
      "end": 625.677,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the Jews who were scattered upon all the face of the earth,",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 209
    },
    {
      "start": 625.857,
      "end": 627.761,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the records of the prophets",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 210
    },
    {
      "start": 627.941,
      "end": 631.052,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and of the twelve apostles of the Lamb are true.",
      "verse": "13:39",
      "lineIndex": 211
    },
    {
      "start": 631.732,
      "end": 633.915,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel spake unto me, saying:",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 212
    },
    {
      "start": 634.095,
      "end": 635.581,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "These last records,",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 213
    },
    {
      "start": 635.761,
      "end": 638.501,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which thou hast seen among the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 214
    },
    {
      "start": 638.681,
      "end": 641.375,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall establish the truth of the first,",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 215
    },
    {
      "start": 641.555,
      "end": 644.063,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are of the twelve apostles of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 216
    },
    {
      "start": 644.243,
      "end": 647.865,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall make known the plain and precious things",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 217
    },
    {
      "start": 648.045,
      "end": 650.413,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which have been taken away from them;",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 218
    },
    {
      "start": 650.593,
      "end": 654.308,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall make known to all kindreds, tongues, and people,",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 219
    },
    {
      "start": 654.488,
      "end": 657.925,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lamb of God is the Son of the Eternal Father,",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 220
    },
    {
      "start": 658.105,
      "end": 659.963,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Savior of the world;",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 221
    },
    {
      "start": 660.143,
      "end": 662.326,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that all men must come unto him,",
      "verse": "13:40",
      "lineIndex": 222
    },
    {
      "start": 662.506,
      "end": 664.085,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or they cannot be saved.",
      "verse": "13:40",
